      </p>
      <p> </p>
      <p>
         <b>Advanced Editor</b>
      </p>
      <p>Go to the Advanced Editor&gt;UX&gt;Branding
    tab. 
    
    <image href="../appsheethelp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/article_attachments/204891237/Screen_Shot_2016-01-13_at_5.05.20_PM.png">
