      <p> </p>
      <p><!--Original: <span @class=wysiwyg-font-size-large>-->
         <ph outputclass="wysiwyg-font-size-large">
            <b>Changing fonts
    and font sizes</b>
         </ph>
      </p>
      <p>Using the Advanced Editor&gt;UX&gt;Options tab, you can
    choose from a set of available fonts and also modify the font
    size.</p>
